    "long_instructions": "####<i class=\"fa-solid fa-drum\"></i> The beat repeats!\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Add drum and bass sounds to define the [beat](#clickable=hint_block) function.\r\n2. Press Run. The sounds will play every time the `beat` function is called.\r\n\r\n---\r\n*Example timeline:*\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/1fcec58260addb806ab12a9d3af86304-image-1744664200641.png)",
